  "summary": "This document is a Competition Notice issued under the PNRR program, funded by the European Union's Next Generation EU initiative, specifically concerning scholarships for university access for the academic year 2025/2026. Its main purpose is to provide detailed information on the assignment of various student benefits, including scholarships and accommodation, outlining eligibility, application procedures, and merit and economic requirements. Key topics covered include types and durations of benefits, definitions of eligible students, online application instructions, merit criteria for different student categories, and economic assessment methods.",
